window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>After a soul-crushing Tinder date, a woman returns to her apartment to cook some squid and seethe. Her eye starts to itch; her memory starts to skip, and she starts to spiral. <i>Offense </i>is an auditory explosion and an exploration of the rash of loneliness...and what happens when the voices inside our heads start to warp.&nbsp;</p>"; 
